What's ALREADY done in tree (contrary to a fresh-read assumption): the 'surface chosen strategy ... in logs' requirement is well-covered at src/indexer/mod.rs — tracing::info! at line 10074 logs page_prep_worker_count / work_queue_capacity / result_queue_capacity / pipeline_channel_size at rebuild start; the downstream pages log 'lexical rebuild prep profile' (line 9963), 'prepared bounded page' (9828), and budget-shrink decisions. The rebuild config IS currently observable; what's missing is the adaptation loop that would change those values based on observed PSI / load / commit latency pressure.

